title: Kubernetes: Cluster Collector
agents: kubernetes
catalog: containerization/kubernetes
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 The connection status to the Kubernetes API is implicitly reported by the
 Checkmk service. This check reports the connection status of the Cluster
 Collector deployed in the Kubernetes cluster. It also reports any problems
 which may arise during processing of the collected performance metrics.

discovery:
 One service is created if the cluster collector option is configured.
